\id 1CO - Sembeleke (SGI1CO.01) Samberigi PNG 1 Corinth 01 5/2/91 Macnaughtan 
\h 1 KOTINDI 
\toc1 Polomaęž‰ Kotindi Siosi paęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee 
\toc2 1 Kotindi 
\toc3 1 Kotindi 
\mt1 Polomaęž‰ Kotindi Siosi paęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki pitolo hataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ aposolo hali hano laęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ± Polomaęž‰ make nikaęž‰ kame Sosenisimaęž‰ make dikanaęž‰maęž‰ tapaasopaęž‰ wape doe.   
\p
\v 2 Iki Kotindi daoni paęž‰taęž‰ haleme Kodaęž‰naęž‰ siosi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ wape polo pi doe. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yakopiki wandaęž‰hali haminaęž‰ wi laęž‰laęž‰me. Iki mo Yesu Ketiso yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰eki haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰me. Kutupa mo kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ nikaęž‰ Tekehali make ikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ biki wi aleme wandaęž‰hali make iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ wape polo pi doe.   
\p
\v 3 Nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso yaapomaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki lopaęž‰niawaenaęž‰e laa alopaęž‰me.   
\s1 Ketiso yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hamono Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki epealaęž‰ ekimanu  
\p
\v 4 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki handolo hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi lo halome.  
\v 5 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketiso yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ hamoko halememe. Pi alemeeki paeyao make hone witelemeeki paeyao make apaęž‰taaso hataęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ hamoko halememe.  
\v 6-7 Hande Ketisonaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wopu daĚ±oĚ±la miniki halememe. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso peneme yaenaęž‰yeke handeteke hataęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ epeaasaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lalememe.  
\v 8 Kutupa ame kini pua pea pa mo paelo paęž‰laęž‰ Natenaęž‰ epenaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki wopu daĚ±oĚ±la haatiki puemenaęž‰ laęž‰tiki pu halieke. Koto mo nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ Natenaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ eki hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wilieke loaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Mo Yesu Ketiso nikaęž‰ Tekehali yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni puemenaęž‰ yeke wi laęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pimanu na tunkuliki otaęž‰ pilieke. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Siosi wandaęž‰hali kaęž‰taalualu pea haemekeeki  
\p
\v 10 Kametonuo. Nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do haumanu puemenaęž‰ do honke alome. Kaęž‰taęž‰ alualu pea na hake pi homekenaęž‰ kake mandakenaęž‰ wia hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa make homeke hone wiataęž‰ homeke hau puluekemaęž‰ iki paeyao otaęž‰ tunao hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 11 Kametitio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ Kolaunaęž‰ tapakemaęž‰ la kimieki loaęž‰me. Paeyaomaęž‰ ape ape lo halememe leme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do ekinaęž‰ alome. Iki paeyao homeke homekemaęž‰ la la pu alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Polonaęž‰ halie o IĚ±taęž‰ Apolosinaęž‰ halie o IĚ±taęž‰ Pidanaęž‰ halie o IĚ±taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ halie laa la alualu pitelememe.  
\v 13 Ketisotaęž‰ tunkulaęž‰ alualu pea halemekea. Mo hande aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ Polo mea pua endiaemekepe. Polonaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ bapitaisi pimipe.   
\p
\v 14 Iki paeyao bapitaisi na puake pa Kitisipusi pitaęž‰ Kaiasi yaapo homeke peaowaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi alome.  
\v 15 Kutu puaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Polonaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ IĚ± bapitaisi peaeyaęž‰me laamaęž‰naęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Kutupa make mo hande Sitepanisi ipikaęž‰ weki wandaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± iki bapitaisi peaowaęž‰pate pa mandane wandaęž‰hali bapitaisi peaowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone na witolome.  
\v 17 Ketisomaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali bapitaisi pealuekemaęž‰ na tapaeyaęž‰pate hande Pi Seliapo walonoyeke tapaeyaęž‰me. Kutupa mo hande aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ Ketiso endiaemeke ekinaęž‰ pi manu ulaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa tunkulaamaęž‰naęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hande Pi Seliapotaęž‰ mo kenke haliwekimaęž‰ hone witeleme tupaęž‰ walonoyeke IĚ± na tapaeyaęž‰me.   
\s1 Ketisotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo  
\p
\v 18 Hoke haunaęž‰ alupulu paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ hande aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ endiaemeke pi paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Pa ekie alemepate pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mea daęž‰taasaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ do pi paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekie alomaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Pa ekipeke mo Baibolo buka paęž‰taęž‰ do wape paęž‰laęž‰eki ulaęž‰me.  
\q1 Mo hone wotu witeme haliwekinaęž‰ hone wotu witeme ekitaęž‰ hoeyaalueke.  
\q1 Kutupa mo wape paęž‰laęž‰eki wotu handeleme haliwekinaęž‰ handeleme ekimanu make teaęž‰ nane mea winaęž‰ lolueke laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande hone wotu witeme haliwekitaęž‰ ekipape o mo hande wape paęž‰laęž‰eki wopu handeleme haliwekitaęž‰ ekipape o do kenkenaęž‰ mo pi hotiaęž‰laęž‰meeki wotu handeleme haliwekitaęž‰ ekipape. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ walolotaęž‰ Do kenkenaęž‰ hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Pa alee laa walaęž‰leke handa loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 21 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hone wotu witeleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki handaapaęž‰naęž‰ yeke saęž‰saęž‰ piekeme. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ do nikanaęž‰maęž‰ walo halomaęž‰ pi paęž‰taęž‰ Pa ekie alemepate pa mo opiteleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mea daęž‰taasaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Na hando halomaęž‰eki handomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ opulumeke laa alememe. Kutupa hande Kitiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ hone wotu witemeeki weitelememe.  
\v 23 Kutu pelemepatetaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ Ketiso endiaemekeme laa pi walo halomaęž‰me. Do walomaęž‰ pinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ya handaęž‰olu bepi pu halememe. Kutupa mo Kitiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ Pa ekie lo halememe.  
\v 24 Koto lo halemepate pa mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wi la maęž‰laęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰hali make Diendaili wandaęž‰hali make koto wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ do pinaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo halaęž‰me lo halomaęž‰me.  
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ kenke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ Pa ekie alemepate pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone witaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke haliwekinaęž‰eki lu ankulalaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo kenke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ damako pupa ulaęž‰ ekie alemepate pa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke haliwekinaęž‰eki lu ankulalaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 26 Kametitio. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki wi leaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ haeme ekitaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Mo kenke haliwekimaęž‰ handeleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ pa peao paeyao hone wopu wiki haliweki na haememe.  
\v 27 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hone wotu wiki haliweki yaalaęž‰ mea peaaluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pa pi aleme ekimanu ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰naęž‰ hone wia miekeme. Kutupa make mo hamoko haliweki yaalaęž‰ mea peaaluekemaęž‰ mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ damakopiki ekie alemeeki kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰naęž‰ hone wia miekeme.  
\v 28 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ tumiki haumanu hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰niaasemeeki make pa alemanue laa hone witelemeeki make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰naęž‰ hone wia miekeme.  
\v 29 Koto mo hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hakoko na linaęž‰yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kutu piekeme.  
\v 30 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki mea Yesu Ketiso yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pealaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone wopu witaęž‰laęž‰eki haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa make Ketisomaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaapo tikitiki yao hamono laataęž‰ nikitaęž‰ yakopiki wandaęž‰hali hamono laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make niki pa kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalaęž‰me.  
\v 31 Kutu pieke handaa mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ peaęž‰pekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa Hali epimaęž‰ hakoko luekemaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ peaalaęž‰ ekimanu hone witolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hakoko liaęž‰peke yelieke wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\c 2  
\s1 Ketisotaęž‰ aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ tamendiao hayeke pi  
\p
\v 1 Ya kametitio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi waluekemaęž‰ epoaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo yaka waloaęž‰ pi make yaka hone witoloeki make mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pa anaęž‰naęž‰ opuaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ pi kone waloaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Kutupa iki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ hone dupa uaęž‰me. Mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao hone yonkaęž‰laaso hataęž‰ pa mo Yesu Ketiso pitaęž‰ mo hande ipiki aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ endiaemekeeki yaapo homeke waluekemaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ haowaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Kutupa make iki paęž‰taęž‰ epoaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ damako pupa wia paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ puki laęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ piaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰ mo hone wopu witeme kenke haliwekimaęž‰ aleme tupaęž‰ pi hokulu hokulu na loaęž‰pate pa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ wele wopupiki honkopu peneme yaenaęž‰yeke waloaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaaleme ekitaęž‰ pa mo kenke halinaęž‰ hone wotu witemeeki opitolo hataęž‰ na tulaalemepate pa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kone hone tulaalememe.   
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 6 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pinaęž‰ keileke haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hone wotu witolo hataęž‰ pi walo halopate pa do kenkenaęž‰ hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu na lo halome. Do kenkenaęž‰ kilu tombuao haleme haliwekinaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ make loaęž‰me. Koto haliwekinaęž‰ kilu tombuaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ natemanu paelieke.  
\v 7 Kutu piliaęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ hande hone wotu witolo hataęž‰ lo halo ekitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰eki kone alopate pa do kenkenaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pa pankaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekie. Ambaęž‰ do kenke alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao aĚ±iĚ± na wepiki hataęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ niki handaęž‰ mea poluekemaęž‰ do hande hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ hone wiekeme.  
\v 8 Do kenke kilu tombuao haleme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ do hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na handemekeme. Handemekaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ hande paĚ±aĚ± piki Tekehalitaęž‰ mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ na endiaalo pimime.  
\v 9 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate hande Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰taęž‰  
\q1 Wandaęž‰hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na handeekeeki make na opiekeeki make honemaęž‰ na niminaeyekeeki make kotoeki kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ peaeyekeme laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ koto ekimanu kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ peneme yaenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Mo Sipitidimaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao akolopa mu tia pominolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ kaęž‰naęž‰ honemaęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ ekimanu kone handaęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 Hali homekemaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ hone na handaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo somenaęž‰ hone teke paęž‰taęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ hone manutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ temoko homekemaęž‰ kone hando halaęž‰me. Koto tupaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paeyao hando halaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki handomono na laęž‰laęž‰pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu paeyao handomonoyeke ipikaęž‰ Sipitidi kone ambaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ hande Sipitidi meleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu walolo hataęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hone wotu wiki haliwekimaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰eki na walomaęž‰pate pa mo Sipitidimaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰eki walaęž‰tiki pu halomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 14 Koto polomaęž‰pate hande Sipitidi na maęž‰laęž‰ some epitaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ pa kitaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu na miaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupiki sometaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ pa kitaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu na minolo hataęž‰ yalo Pa ekie laa hone na u halaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidi maęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ mo piteme hau paeyao hando kaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hando kaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 16 Hande Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa  
\q1 Tekehalinaęž‰ hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki hali epimaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰pe. Hali epimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ Doeki pie laa lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\m Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate nikanaęž‰maęž‰ witolomaęž‰ honetaęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone witolomaęž‰me.   
\c 3  
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki  
\p
\v 1 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ya kametitio. IĚ±maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi meleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ lo halomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰leke handaa pa mo kenke wandaęž‰hali haememe o mo Ketisonaęž‰ panake weki wandikisunu haememe laa hone witolo hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi waloaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ takaęž‰lake nemanu napeke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ andu kone kuaęž‰me. Kutupa ame do make ikitaęž‰ pa kenke wandaęž‰hali leke haleme ekinaęž‰ takaęž‰lake ne manutaęž‰ pa napeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 3 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ne tunkulaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu make ape alaęž‰ ekimanu make kutupiki haumanu piteleme ekitaęž‰ mo kenke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pu haleme tupaęž‰ kone pitelememe.  
\v 4 Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Polonaęž‰ hali halome la alaęž‰pate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Apolosinaęž‰ hali halome la leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto lo haleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kenke hau na pitelemepe.   
\p
\v 5 Kotaęž‰ Apolositaęž‰ epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. IĚ± Polo make epi yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe. Diki telipinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasopaęž‰ hali yaapo hataęž‰ mo pitolopaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaalememe. Tekehalimaęž‰ diki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰piki e telipaleke handaa pokaasopaęž‰me.  
\v 6 IĚ±taęž‰ wae nokaęž‰polo hali haowaęž‰me. Kutupa Apolosimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikali naa halaęž‰laęž‰ hali hayaęž‰me. Dikitaęž‰ kutu pupaęž‰pate opaake hautaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 7 Wae nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ hali make ikali naa halaęž‰laęž‰ hali make ipilikitaęž‰ biki diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate hande wae ale opaake hautaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ peaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki tieke ulaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Kutupa wae nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ hali make ikali naa halaęž‰laęž‰ hali make taęž‰taęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pate ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasepe ekitaęž‰ yenki make anaęž‰naęž‰ kone milipipikie.  
\v 9 Dikitaęž‰ mandake paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasomaęž‰ haliweki halopaęž‰me. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e kone halememe.  
\p Kutupa ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ da make halememe.  
\v 10 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa kitaęž‰laęž‰eki meataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo da aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone wotu wiki kapenda you hali hataęž‰ pinki ambaęž‰ nokopolome. Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ da aęž‰eluekemaęž‰ mo pinkimanu manda aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo da aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰taęž‰ wotu handeteke hataęž‰ aęž‰eyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa anaęž‰ pilieke.  
\v 11 Do alo pitaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Mo hande da pinkimanu nokopaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu Ketiso homeke ambaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mandane pinki manutaęž‰ nokaęž‰peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 12 Kutupa mo hande pinkimanu manda da aęž‰eluekemaęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ kolomaęž‰ make silipamaęž‰ make yenki tieke toopimaęž‰ make aęž‰elimikie. Kutupa mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ timaęž‰ make yenki katakemaęž‰ make liki manumaęž‰ make da aęž‰elimikie.  
\v 13 Kutu pilimipate pa mo hande pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ Nate epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo da aęž‰eleme haliweki paeyaonaęž‰ aęž‰eleme hau manutaęž‰ peneme yaalieke. Koto Natenaęž‰taęž‰ mo ti talaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ kone ipilieke. Kutupa haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ aęž‰elemeeki manutaęž‰ mo hande ti tolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ kone ta handilieke.  
\v 14 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande pinki manda aęž‰elaęž‰eki na teke paa hao hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto da aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ epeke yenki milieke.  
\v 15 Kutu piliepate pa mo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰elaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ to paeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰elaęž‰eki paeyao alupalieke. Hande aęž‰eyeke sometaęž‰ na alupiki daęž‰taa haliepate pa ti talaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ kone pindi pitaęž‰laęž‰ hali leke daęž‰taa halieke.   
\p
\v 16 Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ yakopiki da haminaęž‰taęž‰ kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidi iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ pitaalaęž‰eki make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone na witelemepe.  
\v 17 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ yakopiki da hoeyaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto hali hoeyaalieke. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ dataęž‰ yakopiki da yaęž‰leke handa loaęž‰me. Kutupa iki kone ipikaęž‰ yakopiki da halememe.   
\p
\v 18 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki kone na makeaapaęž‰peke. Iki ameĚ±leĚ± hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ tiaotaęž‰ kenke haliwekimaęž‰ hone witeleme tupaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hone wotu ulu hali halome laa leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰eki handaęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hone na wiki hali halome laa ambaęž‰la lapeke aleo.  
\v 19 IĚ±maęž‰ do alo pitaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Kenke haliwekinaęž‰ hone wopu witelemeeki manutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handaataęž‰ hone na wiki pa ekie laa lelieke. Mo Baibolonaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki dupa.  
\q1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo kenkenaęž‰ hone wotu witeleme haliwekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone wotu witelemeeki manumaęž‰taęž‰ iki kone honaęž‰ meao taminaęž‰ lelieke laa laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\m
\v 20 Kutupa mo Baibolonaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa.  
\q1 Kenke haliwekinaęž‰ hone wopu witelemeeki manutaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ handa alotaęž‰ Pa alemanu witelememe laa laęž‰laęž‰me wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\m
\v 21 Koto ekinaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo kenke haliwekimaęž‰ hone wia piteleme ekimanu handolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi laapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ mo Ketiso tapake ikaęž‰eki yaęž‰leke handa loaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Polo make Apolosi make Pida make do kenke paeyao make mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo make ame do pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make wetepe pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki make do ekimanu paeyao ikaęž‰eki yaęž‰laęž‰pate  
\v 23 ikitaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ekie. Kutupa Ketisotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰eki halaęž‰me.   
\c 4  
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ aposolo haliweki  
\p
\v 1 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ hone dupa wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ikitaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaasomaęž‰ haliweki hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ haumanu handeteke haleme haliwekie laa hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 2 Mo e pokaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hau pitelemeeki homeke homeke weiyu haleme ekitaęž‰ dupa. Ikaęž‰ teke halinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ na tunkuliki ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰eki paeyao opua piteleme ekinaęž‰ weiyu halememe.  
\v 3 Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mandane haliwekimaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ polo ekinaęž‰ pi yokaalu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone witolo koto ekitaęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰me hone witolome. Pa IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make yaka ekinaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ ya kone pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ hone na witolome.  
\v 4 IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na handolopate pa koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Epeke halie pi lapeke anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke yaka haunaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaęž‰peke halitaęž‰ mo Tekehali homekee.  
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ Nate epenaęž‰yeke handeteke hataęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰eki ambaęž‰la pi yokaalu na peke pa handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Tekehalimaęž‰ epenaęž‰ yu wia hapaęž‰peke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo timbaęž‰ lekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰eki paeyaotaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ mea wilieke. Kutupa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ puki nane pankaęž‰ ulaęž‰ honemanu ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ peneme yaalieke. Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ pimi ekinaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ meaęž‰peke ekimanu handolo hataęž‰ ikinaęž‰ pi la wilieke.   
\p
\v 6 Kametitio. Do wape pitolo pi paeyaotaęž‰ mo Apolosi diki paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ puaęž‰me. Dikanaęž‰maęž‰ pitolopaęž‰ hau manunaęž‰ wape polo ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ lombei peaamaęž‰naęž‰yeke puaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyaaso hataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ biki lu mininiaasemeeki na peaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 7 Neketaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ankulao tieke halenaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰pe. Nakaęž‰ wia haleeki paeyaotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ na kiaęž‰pe. Koto paęž‰laęž‰eki yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ya kone polomaęž‰ alaęž‰ halimaęž‰ laataęž‰ nakaęž‰ biki kone ekipeke mea aęž‰meiyaasepe.   
\p
\v 8 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ ambaęž‰ melememe. Ikitaęž‰ hamoko haliweki ambaęž‰ halememe. Ikitaęž‰ mo kini haliweki leke hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ halemepate pa nikitaęž‰ yonkaęž‰lao pelememe. Aęž‰taęž‰e. Yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki otaęž‰ kini haliweki haminaęž‰ alome. Kutu pu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ niki make iki ameĚ±leĚ± kini haliweki halumeke.  
\v 9 Pate ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aposolo haliweki nikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoki nane hamono laęž‰laęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ mo homaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ handele tupaęž‰ mo kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ leke popeleke nane make mo enisolo tapakenaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ make otaęž‰ mo telepo laęž‰tiaasaęž‰ hama tukikinaęž‰ homaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki tupaęž‰ halomaęž‰eki handelememe.  
\v 10 Ketisonaęž‰ biki daeyaenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ hone na wiki haliweki halomaęž‰pate ikitaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ haunaęž‰ hone wotu wilimi haliweki halememe. Nikitaęž‰ honkopu na halomaęž‰pate ikitaęž‰ honkopu wotu halememe. Ikaęž‰ biki laasemepate pa niki paęž‰taęž‰ biki na ulaęž‰ haliwekie la alememe.  
\v 11 Ambaęž‰ make ame make nikitaęž‰ ne ikali teaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰tiki pu hataęž‰ mo dau make wotu diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki halomaęž‰me. Haliwekimaęž‰ niki pa litolo ombu haenaęž‰ make kutupa otaęž‰ nikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ na hake pa pominolo hataęž‰taęž‰  
\v 12 nikaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ kone mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰piki e wotu pokaęž‰tiki pu halomaęž‰me. Kutupa niki kitaaseme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ epeke wamopiki pimaęž‰ kone epeaasomaęž‰me. Tanda pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu ku halemeeki make pa meatiao pu halomaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Niki laaseme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make epeke pimanu lo hombo peaasomaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ ne sambe baasaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me. Kutupa ambaęž‰ make ame make nikitaęž‰ do kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ haĚ±iĚ± taĚ±laĚ±ęž‰laĚ±ęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 14 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do wape polo ekitaęž‰ iki yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homaaluekemaęž‰ na puaęž‰me. Pate ikitaęž‰ yaka weki wandiki leke haleme ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tikitiki yaluekemaęž‰ puaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Ikaęž‰ Ketiso haleme ekinaęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekitaęž‰ mo 10 daosenimanu mea haenaęž‰ lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰pate pa ikaęž‰ apaęž‰taęž‰ homekee. Ikaęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ haleme ekinaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ halome. Koto mo Pi Seliapo iki paęž‰taęž‰ mea epolo ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupaęž‰pe laa IĚ±maęž‰ honke tieke alome. IĚ±maęž‰ pitoloeki mokaęž‰la hataęž‰ kone pipe la alome.  
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰yeke hande Timoditaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaasome. Ipikitaęž‰ yaka pukimaęž‰ homolo weki hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Ketiso halaęž‰eki make otaęž‰eki halaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ Ketiso hataęž‰ hau pu haloeki make mo siosi paeyaonaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ walo haloeki make Timodimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paa u tiaalieke.   
\p
\v 18 Iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Polotaęž‰ paa na ipilieke laa hone witolo hataęž‰ Nikaęž‰ kone anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me laa hone wia halememe.  
\v 19 Pate Tekehalimaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ koto kone paa ipulueke. Paa epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Niki kone anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me aleme haliwekinaęž‰ pa alemeeki manutaęž‰ hone na wiki ikaęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ peaęž‰pekeeki manutaęž‰ pa aęž‰pa handa weilueke.  
\v 20 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa pimaęž‰ alaęž‰eki diaęž‰pate otaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki homekee.  
\v 21 Do hone paęž‰laęž‰eki yaapotaęž‰ handoeki hone pelemepe. Iki tikitiki yaluekemaęž‰ tolo mea mina eponope o yopu hataęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ eponope.   
\c 5  
\s1 Loke hoeyaeyeke hautaęž‰ Siosi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ wiekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰ hoeyaasaęž‰ hau iki ameĚ±leĚ± ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ opolome. Kutupa mo kutu piki hautaęž‰ mo pi na miki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ make na pu haleme hau kone paęž‰laęž‰me. Hande hautaęž‰ dupa. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ wandaęž‰ kone maęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Niki kone anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me la aleme ekitaęž‰ ekipa alemepe. Epeke ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutupiki haunaęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ eĚ± lapaęž‰peke aleo. Kutupa mo hande hau pieke halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mombelemeeki minaęž‰paęž‰lao yokaęž‰paęž‰peke aleo.   
\p
\v 3 IĚ±taęž‰ yaka loke haotaęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane papate halopate yaka temokomaęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake hataęž‰ lolo puaęž‰ tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Tekehali Yesu ipikaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ mo hande pambaęž‰ na piki hau pieke hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi ambaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Iki mombela haminaęž‰ IĚ± make ya temoko kone iki ameĚ±leĚ± haminaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo Tekehali Yesunaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki niki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ taĚ±lolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰  
\v 5 hande Tekehalinaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ Natenaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ temoko daęž‰taenaęž‰yeke ametaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke hoeyaenaęž‰yeke Sadani paęž‰taęž‰ halomanaęž‰ alome.   
\p
\v 6 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Niki kone anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me la aleme ekitaęž‰ popeke na piki pi alememe. Hande opeleme lo halemeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupa. Mo pombei yaasaęž‰ yisititaęž‰ hosiki alesikimaęž‰ kone palaowa paeyao pombei yao halaęž‰me laa lo halememe.  
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki kone otaęž‰ wamo pea haluekemaęž‰ do ambaęž‰ wieke hoke haunaęž‰ pombei yaasaęž‰ yisititaęž‰ otaęž‰ yokaęž‰ mea baapaęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ pombei na yaake panake palaowamaęž‰ handilimikie. Kutu pikieki ame do pelememe. Pa ekipeke Ketisotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeekeeki maęž‰naęž‰siki leke ambaęž‰ lia haleeke ekinaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeeke ekinaęž‰ ne pambaalo polomaęž‰eki ame do anaęž‰naęž‰ ulaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande nikaęž‰ Lombei Pupa Yapeeke ekinaęž‰ ne pambuluekemaęž‰ hande ambaęž‰ pombei yaalaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu pitaęž‰ hoeyaapeke ekimanu yaaponaęž‰ yisiti ulaęž‰ palaowa na mumanaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pate mo hande na pombei yaake palaowa mumanaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke aleo. Koto palaowataęž‰ otaęž‰eki yalo hokeeki taapunaęž‰ diaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 9 Ambaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaowaęž‰ wape paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo tooli kaęž‰taaseme wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± na hapaęž‰peke laa loaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Koto loaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hande pi na miki hataęž‰ tooli kaęž‰taaseme wandaęž‰hali make o mo pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu yambeleme wandaęž‰hali make o toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaaseme wandaęž‰hali make hande pitaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ na loaęž‰me. Koto wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± na haluekemaęž‰ yeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenke aĚ±iĚ± minaęž‰paęž‰lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 IĚ±maęž‰ loaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Ketiso kamee la alaęž‰pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tooli kaęž‰taasaęž‰ hau o honumake hau o toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaasaęž‰ hau o pi la la pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau o hoke ikali naa keaasaęž‰ hau o pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu yambaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ hau pa pulu ombu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutupiki hali ameĚ±leĚ± na hapaęž‰peke loaęž‰me. Kutu piki hali ameĚ±leĚ± mandake paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitaęž‰ kone ne na napaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 12 Pate pi na miki hamaęž‰ nane haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ yaka e diaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰ homekemaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaalieke. Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ peaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 13 Hande Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupa. Hande hoke halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mombeleme paęž‰taęž‰ na pitinaęž‰ leke pa yokaa taęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\c 6  
\s1 Ketiso kame titimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi yokaalunaęž‰ hatuku pemekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Iki ameĚ±leĚ± hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Ketiso yankeke paęž‰taęž‰ eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki handaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ na epeaake pa mo pi na miki pi yokaalu handeteke haleme haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ pua leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homiliepe.  
\v 2 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu polomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone na witelemepe. Mo kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰eki peaęž‰paęž‰peke yeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo iki ameĚ±leĚ± opolo pa hosikieki manutaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi yokaalu peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 3 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo enisolo titinaęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu polomaęž‰eki make hone na witelemepe. Kutu pulu polomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ halomaęž‰eki manunaęž‰ kone anaęž‰naęž‰ pi yokaalu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa loaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo hande haumanu iki tukikinaęž‰ opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pi na miki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mea pelimikipe.  
\v 5 Do alo pitaęž‰ iki yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homaaluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ epeke hone witaęž‰laęž‰ hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na halaęž‰pe. Kutu piki halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Ketiso hameke yaaponaęž‰ pi yokaalu pitelepeeki epeaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 6 Koto hau na piki pa Ketiso hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Ketiso yankeke kone pi yokaalunaęž‰ mea puataęž‰ pa mo pi na miki haliwekimaęž‰ kone ipilikaęž‰ pi yokaalu peaenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa iki kone pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ mea pulimieki manutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki otaęž‰ lopa halememe laa peneme yaasaęž‰me. Mo iki hoeyaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ pa winaęž‰ paapaęž‰peke alee. Kutupa mo pake nalaęž‰ ekimanu make pa winaęž‰ paapaęž‰peke alee.  
\v 8 Kutu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na piki ikaęž‰ kone hoeya alualu pea pake naa alualu pea ikaęž‰ yankeketiti paęž‰taęž‰ kone pitelememe.  
\v 9 Hande hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone na witelemepe. Ikaęž‰ kone na makeaapaęž‰peke. Mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ loke hoeyao haleme wandaęž‰hali make toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniao haleme wandaęž‰hali make tooli kaęž‰tao haleme wandaęž‰hali make mo wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kone pu haleme haliweki make kutupu haleme wandaęž‰weki make  
\v 10 mo pake no haleme wandaęž‰hali make pasaęž‰tei hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali make kutupa hoke ikali naa keao haleme wandaęž‰hali make pi la la pu haleme wandaęž‰hali make dupiki hau pu haleme wandaęž‰hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ na pelieke.  
\v 11 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ kutupiki wandaęž‰hali haemepate pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu tandaęž‰ pea haenaęž‰ yeke handa ametaęž‰ wamo pea halememe. Ametaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki talopu mea haminaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa ame ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao haminaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupiki hautaęž‰ mo Tekehali Yesu Ketiso pitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidi yaapomaęž‰ peaalaęž‰me.   
\s1 Ikaęž‰ loke manumaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyaapekeeki  
\p
\v 12 Hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ya hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau paeyao peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa leliepate pa mo hau paeyao pitolomaęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ niki epeaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hau paeyao peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo hau homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitolo ekimaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ hali leke hano lenaęž‰ otaęž‰ na lolueke laa loaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ne nalaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ welekenaęž‰ ekie laataęž‰ Pa mo weleke make ne muluekemaęž‰ halaęž‰me laa lelie ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate koto ale yaapo telipinaęž‰ homeke dinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paeyaalieke. Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yeke homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokemaęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰naęž‰ loke hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ na hake pa mo Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokaaluekemaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa make mo Tekehalimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ lokemanu handeteke haluekemaęž‰ halaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Tekehalitaęž‰ otaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ kone mea tiaeyeke ekinaęž‰ kotaęž‰ niki make ipikaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ kone mea tiaalieke.   
\p
\v 15 Ikaęž‰ loke manutaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ tunao hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki kone halemeeki hone na witelemepe. Kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Ketisonaęž‰ loke paęž‰taęž‰ tunao halaęž‰ hali hataęž‰ yaka loke yokaęž‰ meataęž‰ mo mani muluekemaęž‰ hone witaęž‰laęž‰ wandiki maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ loke yaapo apaęž‰taenaęž‰ loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ piliepe. Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Hali epimaęž‰taęž‰ mo mani muluekemaęž‰ hone witaęž‰laęž‰ wandiki yaapo apaęž‰tao halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipilikitaęž‰ homeke loke kone halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone na witelemepe. Koto mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa. Hande yaapotaęž‰ homeke loke kone halipipikie laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 17 Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰pate hali epimaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ temokotaęž‰ homeke kone halipipikie.   
\p
\v 18 Taęž‰taęž‰naęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ na wataake nindi pea hapaęž‰peke. Mandane hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ loke hamaęž‰ nane pitaęž‰laęž‰pate hali epimaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰naęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ haumanu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke paęž‰taęž‰ kone hoke hau peaasaęž‰me  
\v 19 Ikaęž‰ lokemanu tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidi pitinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yakopiki da haleme ekitaęž‰ hone na witelemepe. Kutupa mo Holi Sipitidi pilaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone na witelemepe. Ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰eki diaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰naęž‰eki halememe.  
\v 20 Ipikaęž‰eki kone haminaęž‰yeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ yenki tiekemaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hambaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ loke manumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyaenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ handeteke hapaęž‰peke.   
\c 7  
\s1 Wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande tapaeme wapenaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pimi ekinaęž‰ hombo peaaso pitaęž‰ dupa. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰ na miki pa hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epeke pitaęž‰laęž‰pate  
\v 2 hande wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ haumanu wotu yaęž‰leke handaataęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make wandaęž‰maęž‰ halinaęž‰ da pulaęž‰eki make kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ epelieke.  
\v 3 Halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weteke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ halaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa wandaęž‰maęž‰ make haliki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ halaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 4 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke ipikaęž‰ kone na handeteke halaęž‰pate halikimaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰me. Halimaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ loke ipikaęž‰ kone na handeteke halaęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ wetekemaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Kutupa tooli taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰taęž‰ homekemaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ki paęž‰laęž‰me lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi laęž‰ wia Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰ pao hosiki hapaęž‰naęž‰e laa lepekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pate pa ipilikaęž‰ loke handeteke halepeeki anaęž‰ na pitolo hapinaęž‰ Sadanimaęž‰ ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone mea wiaapaęž‰naęž‰ paa taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 6 Do alo pitaęž‰ la witolo hataęž‰ dupaęž‰pe laa na alopate pa iki puemenaęž‰yeke ikaęž‰ hone pa tikitiki yaowaasome.  
\v 7 Pate iki paeyao IĚ± halo tupaęž‰ haminaęž‰yeke hone paęž‰laęž‰pate pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ telipaasaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pikieki telipao halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 8 Mo wandaęž‰ na miki o hali na peke pa haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make kineke wandaęž‰weki paęž‰taęž‰ make do pi alome. IĚ± halo tupaęž‰ haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke.  
\v 9 Kutu piliepate pa ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ homu peaapeke na yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ wandaęž‰ meaęž‰pekeeki make halinaęž‰ da puaęž‰pekeeki make anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Hone paęž‰laęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰ ti talaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handolo haenaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ hoelieke. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰ mea hali pua pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ epelieke.   
\p
\v 10 Kutupa mo tooli tooli peleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ yakaeki na laake mo Tekehalimaęž‰ dupaęž‰pe alaęž‰eki kone la kitolome. Halinaęž‰ da paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 Pate kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa pua hao hao o hali paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la paa peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make epelieke. Halimaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yokaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ pi diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa IĚ±maęž‰ kone dupa alome. Ketiso hali homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ pi na miki wandaęž‰ hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kutupa mo wandaęž‰taęž‰ haliki yaapo haluekemaęž‰ hone wia hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo halimaęž‰ koto wandaęž‰taęž‰ yokaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 13 Kutupa make mo Ketiso wandaęž‰ homekemaęž‰ pi na miki hali yaapo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kutupa mo halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo haluekemaęž‰ hone wia hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 14 Do alo pitaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Hande pi na miki halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰e alaęž‰me. Kutupa hande pi na miki wandaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Ketiso hali yaapo taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰e alaęž‰me. Do aloeki na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wekiwandiki tititaęž‰ pa mo Kodaęž‰ mataake weki wandiki halo pimime. Kutu pulu pelemepate ametaęž‰ ikaęž‰ weki wandikimanu haleme ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰e alaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Kutu pu hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate hande pi na miki halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Ketiso wandaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao penaęž‰ yeke hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutu pinaęž‰e. Mandake tupaęž‰ kone mo pi na miki wandaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Ketiso hali pa minaęž‰paęž‰laeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutu pinaęž‰e. Koto hau tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hande Ketiso hali paęž‰taęž‰ make Ketiso wandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make potaęž‰ aęž‰mbaapekeeki diaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wi alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaaso hataęž‰ haminaęž‰yeke wi alaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Ketiso wandaęž‰o. Nakaęž‰ haliki tambaęž‰ minolo halenaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Ketiso hali haliepe o na haliepe nakanaęž‰maęž‰ na handeleme. Kutupa Ketiso hali neke make nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minolo halenaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Ketiso wandaęž‰ haliepe o na haliepe nakanaęž‰maęž‰ na handeleme.   
\s1 Iki wi leeke natenaęž‰ haemeke tupaęž‰ kone pa hao hapaęž‰pekeeki  
\p
\v 17 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ telipea pa kitaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu mea wia hataęž‰ make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki wi leeke aęž‰pa haeme tupaęž‰ kone pa hao hapaęž‰peke. Do hande pi ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰tiki pu halome.  
\v 18 Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wi leeke natenaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau pea hataęž‰ opuataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande sekemesaisi hau paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ honialuekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wi leeke natenaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ sekemesaisi hau na piki hataęž‰ opuataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ sekemesaisi hau puluekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 19 Mo hande sekemesaisi hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make na pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make telipinaęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu opua pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kototaęž‰ hau tiekee.  
\v 20 Iki paeyaomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wi leeke natenaęž‰ haemeke tupaęž‰ kone paa hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 21 Neketaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaase hali hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wi leekeeki opipe. Kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ kotoeki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke. Pate nakaęž‰ hande pa hameke e pokaaseeki minaęž‰paęž‰laalenaęž‰ potaęž‰ lombeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 22 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Mo pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki wi alaęž‰eki opuataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ halie. Koto tupaęž‰ kone mo pa halaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ ipiki wi alaęž‰eki opuataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo Ketisonaęž‰ e pa hameke pokaasaęž‰ halie.  
\v 23 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ yenki tiekemaęž‰ iki hambaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ mo haliwekinaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaaseme haliweki na hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 24 Kametitio. Iki paeyaotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki wi leeke natenaęž‰ haeme tupaęž‰ kone pa ame make Kodaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± hao hapaęž‰peke.   
\s1 Wandaęž‰ na miki o hali na peke kutupa kineke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu  
\p
\v 25 Hande wandaęž‰ na miki o hali na peke weki wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ honke leme ekitaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ dupaęž‰pe alaęž‰ pi diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo IĚ±maęž‰ hone witoloeki kone alome. Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo ekinaęž‰ hone tulaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me loaęž‰me.  
\v 26 IĚ±maęž‰ dupa alome. Do hande kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ nate halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo epeke ekitaęž‰ dupa. Homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ame do haleme tupaęž‰ paa haenaęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa hone witolome.  
\v 27 Neketaęž‰ wandaęž‰ melepe. Kotaęž‰ wandaęž‰ yokuluekemaęž‰ hone na wiaęž‰peke. Neketaęž‰ wandaęž‰ na miki haekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ wandaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone na wiaęž‰peke.  
\v 28 Koto alopate pa wandaęž‰ mikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau na piteleme. Kutupa wandiki make halinaęž‰ da peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau na pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto hau peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ tooli tooli haasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ manutaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰paapaęž‰naęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 29 Kametitio. Koto aloeki manutaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Nate wopu diaęž‰yalo haenaęž‰taęž‰ ametaęž‰ wandaęž‰ miki haliwekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰ na miki haleme haliweki tupaęž‰ hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 30 Kutupa eĚ± aleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ eĚ± na leke haleme wandaęž‰hali tupaęž‰ hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa ki taleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ki na teke haleme wandaęž‰hali tupaęž‰ hapaęž‰peke. Kutaa make mo hambaęž‰tiki pu haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ na hambeke wandaęž‰hali leke hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 31 Kutupa kenkenaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ e pokeleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kenkenaęž‰ alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu na wiki wandaęž‰hali leke hapaęž‰peke. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Do hande kenketaęž‰ ame ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ pa na u halieke.   
\p
\v 32 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone eleke eleke u halemeeki manutaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hone na paęž‰laęž‰me. Wandaęž‰ na miki halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu epeke tupaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone u halaęž‰me.  
\v 33 Kutu pu halaęž‰pate mo wandaęž‰ miki halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaaluekemaęž‰yeke do kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ hone u halaęž‰me.  
\v 34 Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ putupa yaapo ualu paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mo halinaęž‰ da na peke wandaęž‰maęž‰ make moputali wandikimaęž‰ make Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone u halaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ loke temoko make Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ yako peaenaęž‰yeke hone wilieke. Kutu piliepate pa mo halinaęž‰ da paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaaluekemaęž‰yeke do kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ hone u halaęž‰me.  
\v 35 IĚ±maęž‰ do alo pi manutaęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰yeke alome. IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ potaęž‰manu saęž‰saęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ na alopate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tikitiki yao hataęž‰ hone eleke eleke na wiki Tekehalinaęž‰ e otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ pokaamaęž‰naęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 36 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ wandiki hapulu paęž‰laęž‰ wale alemanu wia hataęž‰ kone paa na mulueke laa kutupa wetepenaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ honemaęž‰ o ipikaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu mo wandiki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make o ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ honkopu wotu haaso hataęž‰ hapuluekee hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ minaęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 37 Pate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pa ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone honkopu haaso hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ handeteke hapeke yaęž‰leke handaataęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰ wandikitaęž‰ na mulueke alo hataęž‰ dikitaęž‰ na mualu piki pa hao hapanaęž‰e laa hone otaęž‰ na laęž‰kaęž‰leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make epeke hau kone pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 38 Kutupa mo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yenki ulaęž‰ wandiki hapiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ epekeeki pitaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo ipikaęž‰ yenki wilie wandiki na hapilie hali ipikitaęž‰ mo lombeipiki epeke hau tieke pitaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 39 Kutupa mo halinaęž‰ da paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki paa hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki paęž‰taęž‰ hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ haliki homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa otaęž‰ Ketiso halinaęž‰ da peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke.  
\v 40 Koto hau peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ hone witolo ekitaęž‰ dupa. Hande kosaęž‰piki wandaęž‰taęž‰ pa kosaęž‰ piki haekaęž‰naęž‰ make otaęž‰ epelieke hone witolome. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ hone witolopate pa ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitiditaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ make pilaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ do pi alome.   
\c 8  
\s1 Toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ ne halaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Kutupa hande toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ ne halaęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ wape pea lotaęž‰ pimi ekitaęž‰ dupa alome. Niki paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mo handaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me. Pate mo handaęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰taęž‰ mo hakoko litaęž‰laęž‰ hau pu tiaasaęž‰pate pa mo pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ daeya haenaęž‰ alaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ handa ulume laa hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto halinaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 3 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate hali epimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto hali otaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 4 Kutupa mo toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ haleaęž‰ nemanu pa naleme ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa. Mo homeke Kodaęž‰ homeke halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hande toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ aletaęž‰ otaęž‰eki diaęž‰me hone witolomaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Mo wandaęž‰hali manumaęž‰ lo haleme kodaęž‰manu make teke halimanu make oli ya nane hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make do kenke nane hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ make pa pinaęž‰maęž‰  
\v 6 nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ homeke kone nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ hataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao wepia winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halaęž‰me laataęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ti lao halomaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo Tekehali homeke homeketaęž‰ Yesu Ketiso halaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao wepia winaęž‰ laataęž‰ niki make ambaęž‰ daęž‰taalaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Koto do nikanaęž‰maęž‰ handolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ na handelememe. Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ alenaęž‰ haumanu piaęž‰tiki pu haemeke ekinaęž‰ ame make kutupiki nemanu nalo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ alenaęž‰ ekie hone witelememe. Kutu piki wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone na lumba witolo hataęž‰ kone mo hande ne nalomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ niki hoeyaasaęž‰me laa hone witelememe.  
\v 8 Koto tupaęž‰ hone witelemepate pa mo ne nalomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ niki hatuku Kodaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ pu hamono lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mo ne na neke haomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto ekimaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ yonkaęž‰lamono alu na pealieke. Kutupa ne nolo polomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make mandane haumanu apaęž‰tao na mulumeke.   
\p
\v 9 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ handaa pitelemeeki manumaęž‰taęž‰ pa mo hone wopu na tulaaleme wandaęž‰hali hoke hau pea lopaapaęž‰naęž‰yeke wotu handeteke hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 10 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Neketaęž‰ handele hali hataęž‰ pa toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ alenaęž‰ yeni hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pua pitaęž‰ ne naleme ekitaęž‰ mo dupiki haunaęž‰ hone na lumba ulaęž‰ halimaęž‰ neke handeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ pitele ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo toopi ti wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ yeni hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ nemanu nenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ na sutiaalipikipe.  
\v 11 Kutupa do nakaęž‰ handele ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande honkopu na hake halitaęž‰ hoeyaalipikie. Koto halitaęž‰ Ketiso ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hali nakaęž‰ kame kone hoeyaalipikie.  
\v 12 Kutu pitele haumaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ hone wotu na lumba wilimi yankekemanu hoeyaekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ make hoke hau pilipikie.  
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka kamenaęž‰ ne nalaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki hoke hau pinaęž‰ mea lopaapeke yeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo mindiki maęž‰ndaęž‰siki hoto homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na nolueke. Yaka kame lopaapaęž‰naęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.   
\c 9  
\s1 Mo Aposolo halinaęž‰ peaęž‰pekeeki pitaęž‰ meaęž‰pekeeki yaapo  
\p
\v 1 IĚ±taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ taęž‰pao halo hali na halope. IĚ±taęž‰ aposolo hali na halope. Nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu na handoaęž‰pe. Ikitaęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokaaso ekinaęž‰ na halemepe.  
\v 2 Mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ aposolo hali na halome hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa pinaęž‰maęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutupiki hone otaęž‰ wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Iki Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ haleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa IĚ±taęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ aposolo hali haloeki peneme yaasaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 3 Mo IĚ± laaseme haliwekinaęž‰ pimanu hombo peaasoeki dupa alome.  
\v 4 IĚ±taęž‰ yaka enaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ mo ne ikali napekeeki anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 5 Mo mandane aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ make mo Tekehalinaęž‰ hameke titimaęž‰ make Pidamaęž‰ make koto haliwekimaęž‰ piteleme tupaęž‰ IĚ± make Ketiso wandaęž‰ mea hatuku pomuaęž‰peke anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 6 Diaęž‰me mo Banabasi diki yaapo homekemaęž‰ mo yenki mulu paęž‰laęž‰ e pokaęž‰peke ekimaęž‰ kone dikaęž‰ ne alemanu hambaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 7 Hali epimaęž‰ mo ami hali hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ manimaęž‰ kone ipikaęž‰ ne dau hambaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Diaęž‰me. Kutupa mo e teke halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ne kone napeke na yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Kutupa make mo sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰manu handeteke halaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ andu yupa napeke na yaęž‰laęž‰pe.   
\p
\v 8 Do alo ekitaęž‰ mo kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hau pitelemeeki homeke diaęž‰me pa mo Lo Pimanu make homeke pi kone alaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Mosesimaęž‰ hande Lo Pimanu wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ do tupaęž‰ alaęž‰me. Mo kao maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ mo palaowa kilikimanu ambuku mea baaluekemaęž‰ ankemaęž‰ pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kake na tonkaapeke laa laęž‰laęž‰me. Koto laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo maęž‰naęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone witaęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 10 Koto laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ make hone witaęž‰laęž‰pe. Aowe. Niki paęž‰taęž‰ make hone witaęž‰laęž‰me. Kenke awaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ make kiliki talaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ make e pokolo hataęž‰ mo enaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ nemanu anaęž‰naęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone wia e pokaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidinaęž‰ wae alemanu nokopomaęž‰me. Kutupa ame mo kiliki minaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mandane alemanu niki paęž‰taęž‰ kimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 12 Mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu muluekemaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰peke yaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki lombei pitolo hataęž‰ otaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰pe. Diaęž‰me otaęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa na minolomaęž‰me. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Mo Ketisonaęž‰ Pi Seliapo pulaęž‰eki saęž‰saęž‰ peaapaęž‰naęž‰yeke hande kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu paeyao niki honumake sikimaęž‰ wotu mu halomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13 Mo Tembolo da paęž‰taęž‰ e pokeleme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ nemanu mu haleme ekitaęž‰ handelememe. Kutupa hande maęž‰naęž‰ lia olodanaęž‰ wia halo haleme haliweki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mo limi hotekemanu paęž‰taęž‰ mandaneeki mu haleme ekitaęž‰ handelememe.  
\v 14 Koto tupaęž‰ kone mo Tekehalinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki dupae. Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Pi Seliapo walaaseme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ koto e pokolo hataęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ hapeke ekimanu meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 15 Koto laęž‰laęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na molome. Kutupa ame make aletaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do wape otaęž‰ na tapaasome. Kie laapaęž‰naęž‰ IĚ± ambaęž‰la homaęž‰peke aleo. IĚ±maęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± otaęž‰ pa hameke e pokolo ekinaęž‰ pi laaso ekitaęž‰ hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Paeki alaęž‰me laa pi laapaęž‰naęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.  
\v 16 IĚ±maęž‰ hande Pi Seliapo walaaso ekinaęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi IĚ±maęž‰ kone laapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Tekehalimaęž‰ dupie laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kone pitolome. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Pi Seliapo na walaokaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pei IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 17 Yaka e pokolo ekitaęž‰ yaka honemaęž‰ kone wia pokoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo enaęž‰ yenki muluekemaęž‰ hone ulu puaęž‰pate pa yaka hone wia na piki pa mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ waleaęž‰ e kone pokaaso ekinaęž‰taęž‰  
\v 18 kotaęž‰ eki yenki meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Yaka yenkitaęž‰ dupae. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yenki ki pi na leke handaa mo meaęž‰peke alemanu na minolo hataęž‰ hande Pi Seliapo walaasoeki kone kototaęž‰ yaka yenki anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 19 IĚ±taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ pa hameke e pokaaso hali na hake ya kone halome. Kutupu halopate mandane wandaęž‰hali wopu muluekemaęž‰ yaka hone wia kone wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaaso hali halome.  
\v 20 Mo Diu wandaęž‰hali muluekemaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Diu wandaęž‰hali haleme tupaęž‰ kone halome. IĚ±taęž‰ hande Lo Pi manumaęž‰ kilu tombuaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali leke na halopate pa koto tupaęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali muluekemaęž‰ IĚ± make iki haleme tupaęž‰ kone haowaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Koto tupaęž‰ kone mo Diendaili wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali muluekemaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Lo Pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ na haleme tupaęž‰ IĚ± make koto tupaęž‰ halome. Do alo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yambaęž‰laęž‰ hali leke halome pi na leke IĚ±taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ teliolo hali halo ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Mandane detepiki hone tulaaseme wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki muluekemaęž‰ pa detepiki hali leke halome. Koto ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hau paeyaomaęž‰ iki muluekemaęž‰ iki haleme tupaęž‰ kone IĚ± make hatiki pu halome.  
\v 23 Do pitolo ekitaęž‰ hande Pi Seliapo daeyaenaęž‰yeke pitolome. Kutupa koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali epeaasaęž‰eki manunaęž‰ putupiliki maęž‰ndaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ muluekemaęž‰yeke pitolome.   
\p
\v 24 Hande anke telineĚ±li pitaęž‰laęž‰eki ninaęž‰taęž‰ haliweki wopumaęž‰ anke hao pelimipate titinaęž‰ pelie hali homekemaęž‰ epeke yenki pua milieke. Koto hautaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hone wilimime. Koto ekinaęž‰ iki make titinaęž‰ pua epeke yenki muluekemaęž‰ honkopu haaso hataęž‰ anke hao puaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 25 Anke talineĚ±li pulu paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la mokaęž‰la hande hande pitolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu homao takaęž‰lao haenaęž‰yeke pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu piki halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kukutu peaęž‰peke yenki ale muluekemaęž‰ do haumanu pitaęž‰laęž‰pate nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ kukutu na peaęž‰peke yenki ale muluekemaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰me.  
\v 26 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ anke talineĚ±li pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ lekemaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ pea na piki hande opolo polo polo paęž‰taęž‰ handaęž‰ paleke pulume. IĚ±taęž‰ hande epeke hone wiki kiki aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ hali leke hataęž‰ yaka kikimaęž‰ pa mandaęž‰ meaaso na piki otaęž‰eki kone pitolome.  
\v 27 Yaka loketaęž‰ homu peaaluekemaęž‰ yaka kone yumbitolo hataęž‰ pitolome. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wi laęž‰laęž‰ pi walaaso hali halopate pa wetepenaęž‰ IĚ± kone halu peaapaęž‰naęž‰ pitolome.   
\c 10  
\s1 Toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi  
\p
\v 1 Kametitio. Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ ateke amedamaęž‰ Mosesi teliaęž‰ mea pulu haenaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ piekeeki manutaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Koto tapake paeyaotaęž‰ hande ya hapi oto paęž‰taęž‰ hao puaataęž‰ hande dawala Wepiki Ikali tukikinaęž‰ tunkula pua epeke tupaęž‰ mone teaęž‰naęž‰ opolo pemekeme.  
\v 2 Kutupa mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hande ya hapi paęž‰taęž‰ make mo dawala ikali paęž‰taęž‰ make Mosesinaęž‰ anke teliaęž‰ mea pominolo haenaęž‰ iki paeyaotaęž‰ bapitaisi hau pimikime.  
\v 3 Kutupa paeyaomaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ haleeke ne naataęž‰  
\v 4 mo Sipitidimaęž‰ haleeke ikali make nemekeme. Hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ waleeke toopi paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeeke ikali nemekeme. Kutupa mo wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± pomieke toopitaęž‰ Ketiso kone hayekeme.  
\v 5 Kutu pimikipate koto wandaęž‰hali wopunaęž‰ haunaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homeekeme. Kutupa mo hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ ikaęž‰ tokomanu koto paęž‰taęž‰ wiaęž‰tiki pimikime.   
\p
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo tapakemaęž‰ pimikieki manumaęž‰taęž‰ niki mandaęž‰ meaasaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke haumanu puluekemaęž‰ taapemeke tupaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutupiki haumanu peaapaęž‰naęž‰ yeke kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 7 Kutupa iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ yeni hau pimiki tupaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ peaapaęž‰naęž‰ yeke walaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ne ikali naa kealuekemaęž‰ pitimikipate pa hoki nanetaęž‰ mo haliwekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰weki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ hoke telepo la alualu pimikime laa laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 8 Mandane kutupiki haumanu pimiki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ homeke natenaęž‰ kone 23 daoseni homemekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutu piki haumanu na piki pa yankeke maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ loke hoeyaasaęž‰ haumanu na pumanaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 9 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau manumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ piaęž‰ handeeke tupaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hone u tiaaluekemaęž‰ hone na umanaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Mo hande mandane kutupiki hau pimiki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo hoke ketomaęž‰ aweeke ekimaęž‰ homemekeme.  
\v 10 Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi la la na pumanaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Mo hande mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ kutupiki hau pimiki handaataęž‰ mo lu homaasaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ iki liekeme.   
\p
\v 11 Mo hande wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pimiki ekimanu paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mo mandane wandaęž‰hali paeyao mandaęž‰ mealuekemaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa niki paęž‰taęž‰ kinki pinaęž‰yeke ambaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰me. Niki halomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ paeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰leke handa loaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo some epimaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ daĚ±oĚ±la hataęž‰ epeke tiao halome laa hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ lopaapaęž‰naęž‰ wotu hapeke aleo.  
\v 13 Mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ la handaęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pa ipu halaęž‰eki kone ipulaęž‰pate pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yao halaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo iki mea otaęž‰ lombeipiki lopaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ la handaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na epenaęž‰ lelieke. La handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu ipulu haenaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ potaęž‰ pilao iki tambaęž‰ milieke. Mo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ iki honkopu hao anaęž‰naęž‰ haminaęž‰ lelieke.   
\p
\v 14 Otaęž‰ ya kametitio. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mo toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ yeni hau peaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ mina na peaapaęž‰peke.  
\v 15 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone wotu wilimi ekinaęž‰ do pimanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ alome. Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ aloeki opuaataęž‰ teke weiya handaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 16 Hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki epeaalaęž‰ kaponaęž‰ noluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi laa nalo hataęž‰taęž‰ Ketiso ipikaęž‰ we paęž‰taęž‰ na telipaasomaęž‰pe. Kutupa hande pindipindi pea ulaęž‰ palaowa make nalo hataęž‰taęž‰ Ketiso ipikaęž‰ loke mindiki paęž‰taęž‰ na telipaasomaęž‰pe.  
\v 17 Palaowa punka homeke yaęž‰leke handaataęž‰ niki paeyao wotu kone homeke loke mindiki halomaęž‰me. Hande homeke palaowa punka telipaasomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 18 Mo Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pimikieki make hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Hande lia haleeke hoteke ne alemanu nemeke haliwekitaęž‰ mo oloda paęž‰taęž‰ wiekeeki kone na telipaasemepe.  
\v 19 Do alo ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ eki epinaęž‰ alope. Hande toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰ nemanu pitaęž‰ toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale yaaponaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ekie alope.  
\v 20 Diaęž‰me. Do ekinaęž‰ alome. Mo pi na miki haliwekimaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ lia haleme ekitaęž‰ koto Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ na haleke pa mo hoke temokomanu paęž‰taęž‰ kone halememe. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ mo hoke temokomanu ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea haminaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hone na paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 21 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ kapo paęž‰taęž‰ make hoke temokonaęž‰eki apaęž‰tao napeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ teipolonaęž‰ make mo temokonaęž‰eki make apaęž‰tao napeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 22 Pate mo Tekehalimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ hone witolomaęž‰pe. O nikaęž‰ honkopumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰eki lombei paęž‰laęž‰me laa hone witolomaęž‰pe.   
\p
\v 23 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau paeyao pa peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me la alemepate pa ikaęž‰ hau paeyao piteleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki epeaasaęž‰pe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau paeyao pa peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me la alemepate hande hau paeyao pitelemeeki manumaęž‰taęž‰ niki honkopu haasaęž‰ Ketiso wandaęž‰hali hamono na alaęž‰me.  
\v 24 Hali homekemaęž‰ ya siki epeke tupaęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ hone wopu na wiki pa iki paeyaomaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kone epeke tupaęž‰ haenaęž‰yeke hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 25 Mo makedi paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ hoteke mindikimanu ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa hamba napeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu puluekemaęž‰ yeke hone eleke eleke witolo hataęž‰ lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 26 Pa ekipeke mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kenke make kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu paeyao make Tekehalinaęž‰ ekie laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 27 Pi na miki halimaęž‰ Ne nomanaęž‰e laa neke wi leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kutupa nakaęž‰ honemaęž‰ polueke hone wikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pua pita mo kitaęž‰laęž‰ napeke alemanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hone elekeeleke witolo hataęž‰ lotaęž‰ lotaęž‰ na piki pa napeke.  
\v 28 Kutu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do netaęž‰ toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ haleaęž‰ ekie laa leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo neke paęž‰taęž‰ leaęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ make mo hone na lombaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ make hone witolo hataęž‰ koto ne na napeke.  
\v 29 Nakaęž‰ hone lombaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ na alopate mo somenaęž‰ hone na lombaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\p Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ dupa lelieke. Kotaęž‰ mo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ hone na lombaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ do IĚ±taęž‰ hone lombao hataęž‰ pa hone wia peaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ pa ekipeke handeteke haenaęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe laataęž‰  
\v 30 Kutupa make mo yaka ne ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ keiyae pi loaęž‰ ne nalo ekinaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ekipeke IĚ± laasaęž‰pe laa lelieke.   
\p
\v 31 Pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hau paeyao piteleme ekimaęž‰ make mo ne ikali naleme ekimaęž‰ make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki daeyaenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ hau paeyao peaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 32 Kutupa mo Diu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make Diendaili wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ siosi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ mea lopaaluekemaęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ na peaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 33 IĚ±maęž‰ pu haloeki kone peaęž‰paęž‰peke. IĚ±maęž‰ yaka hau paeyao pitolo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaaluekemaęž‰ pitolome. IĚ± kone epeaaluekemaęž‰ hone na piki pa wandaęž‰hali paeyao Kodaęž‰maęž‰ daęž‰tao haenaęž‰yeke epeaaluekemaęž‰ hone u halome.   
\c 11  
\p
\v 1 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ hau mokaęž‰la hando halo tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ pitoloeki kone mokaęž‰la hando hapaęž‰peke.   
\s1 You aęž‰mbao pitaęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 2 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto paeyao IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone wiataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ walolo ekimanu pu haleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki pi laasome.  
\v 3 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate do alo pitaęž‰ wotu opuaęž‰paęž‰peke. Haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ you halaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ youtaęž‰ haliki halaęž‰me. Kutupa Ketisonaęž‰ youtaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you akaęž‰ pambao pi wala o yeni piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homaasaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Kutupa make wandaęž‰ homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you akaęž‰ na dopuaake pi wala o yeni piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki paęž‰taęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homaasaęž‰me. Kutu piki wandaęž‰taęž‰ mo you itiki makole mea bao halaęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 6 Dupiki wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you akaęž‰ na dopuaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ itiki paeyao makole mea baapeke alee. Kutupa wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ you itiki makole mea baasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make itiki tunkulaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau yaęž‰lekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ akaęž‰ dopua hapeke alee.  
\v 7 Halimaęž‰taęž‰ you akaęž‰ na pambao halieke. Pa ekipeke ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ wele pikieki yaaponaęž‰ suĚ±aĚ±suĚ±aĚ± walaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ wele pikieki yaaponaęž‰ suĚ±aĚ±suĚ±aĚ± walaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 8 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hali wepitolotaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ loke paęž‰taęž‰ mea na wepia haenaęž‰ leekepate pa wandaęž‰taęž‰ halinaęž‰ loke paęž‰taęž‰ mea wepia haenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 9 Kutupa make Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ halimaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰yeke na wepia haenaęž‰ leekepate pa mo hali hone witolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰yeke wepia haenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo enisolo tonumaęž‰ halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ haliki paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tombo walolo ipikaęž‰ you akaęž‰ dopuaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 Do pimanu alopate pa ametaęž‰ niki paeyao Tekehali ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰ hali yaapomaęž‰ tambaęž‰ mu alualu pitolo hataęž‰ hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 12 Pa ekipeke wandaęž‰taęž‰ halinaęž‰ loke paęž‰taęž‰ mea wepia haenaęž‰ leekepate ametaęž‰ halitaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ loke paęž‰taęž‰ kini pea ipulaęž‰me. Kutupa alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Wandaęž‰ homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ pa wandaęž‰hali paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ you akaęž‰ na dopiki pa yeni piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hautaęž‰ ti paęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 14 Mo nikaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ halomaęž‰ haumaęž‰ kone niki mandaęž‰ meaasaęž‰eki dupa. Haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ hokulupeke itiki haenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ yaalaęž‰piki haue.  
\v 15 Pate mo wandaęž‰naęž‰ hokulupeke itikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ au laęž‰laęž‰ ekie. Ipikaęž‰ itiki hokulupeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you aęž‰mbaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate pa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ do aloeki manunaęž‰ ape loluekemaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi homeke lolueke. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ siosi tapake paeyao make hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handeke pa IĚ±maęž‰ do aloeki homeke pu halomaęž‰me.   
\s1 Mo hande Tekehalinaęž‰ ne nalaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 17 Mo manaęž‰ pimanu ame do lolo polo ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu haleme ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi na laalueke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ mombaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰taęž‰ iki na epeaasaęž‰pate pa hokeeki kone ipulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 18 IĚ±maęž‰ mandane opitoloeki dupa. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰ mombaęž‰la hataęž‰ kone tekilipa taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea halememe laa alemeeki opitolo hataęž‰ mandaneeki otaęž‰ ekie hone witolome.  
\v 19 Kutupa make mo mandane tekilipa taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pea halemeeki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau piteleme wandaęž‰hali peneme yaluekemaęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ haue laa loaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Kutu piteleme haumaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ homeke paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la hataęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ ne nalaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na nalememe.  
\v 21 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Iki homeke homeke lomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ne kone aĚ±iĚ± nolueke laa pitolo haminaęž‰ kone mo some homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ homa haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hoke ikali naa keaasaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰manu pitaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ ne ikali napeke na yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ siositaęž‰ Pa ekie laataęž‰ mo natehali wandaęž‰hali make yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homaaluekemaęž‰ pitelemepe. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ eki pi lonope. Kutu piteleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi laanope. Diaęž‰me ikaęž‰ pi laapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 23 IĚ±maęž‰ hande waloaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la kiaęž‰me dupa. Tekehali Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ hande timba ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombeeke natenaęž‰taęž‰ hande palaowa mea mina hataęž‰  
\v 24 Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi laataęž‰ pindi pindi pea alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kitolo ya loke mindikie laataęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ do hau peaęž‰tiki pu hapaęž‰peke leekeme.  
\v 25 Koto tupaęž‰ make ne naa paeyeketaęž‰ hande kapo mea mina hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Do kapotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ panake pi laęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ yaka wemaęž‰ wiaasaęž‰me laataęž‰ Nemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ pu hapaęž‰peke laa leekeme.  
\v 26 Do palaowa make do kaponaęž‰ make nalo hataęž‰ Tekehali epenaęž‰yeke ipikaęž‰ homeekeeki walo halimikie.   
\p
\v 27 Koto ekinaęž‰ hali o wandaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ palaowa make ipikaęž‰ kaponaęž‰ make hoke tupaęž‰ hataęž‰ neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ we loke mindiki paęž‰taęž‰ ketete pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 28 Koto ekinaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ piteleme hau ambaęž‰la wotu handaataęž‰ hande palaowa kaponaęž‰ make napaęž‰peke alee.  
\v 29 Hali epimaęž‰ hande palaowa kaponaęž‰ make nalo hataęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ loke mindiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone na wiki neaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto nalo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ kone hoke hau winaęž‰ alaęž‰me.  
\v 30 Koto piteleme ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali woputaęž‰ yeni haa pitao loke damako pu pitao kutupa mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ homelememe.  
\v 31 Nikaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰ haumanu ambaęž‰la talo pea bao handomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ peaasaęž‰eki niki paęž‰taęž‰ na epenaęž‰ lolo piaęž‰me.  
\v 32 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ hao hoeyaasomaęž‰eki handaataęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ miomono leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo kenke wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao hoke yenki meaamaęž‰naęž‰yeke pitaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 33 Kutupa ya kametitio. Iki mombaęž‰la pitaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ ne noluekemaęž‰ paeyao epenaęž‰ laa yuwia pitaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 34 Kutupa ikaęž‰ mombaęž‰la pitaęž‰ pu hoeyaasemeeki Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handaa iki paęž‰taęž‰ eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ peaamaęž‰naęž‰ mo teaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ kone ne napeke alee. Kutupa mo hande mandane peaęž‰pekeeki manutaęž‰ IĚ± aęž‰pa hataęž‰ tikitiki yalueke.   
\c 12  
\s1 Hande Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu  
\p
\v 1 Ya kametitio. Ya hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ otaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰eki manunaęž‰ hone eleke eleke na uemenaęž‰ hone witolome.  
\v 2 Ikitaęž‰ pi na miki haemeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ hande pi lapeke na yeke toopi timaęž‰ wepia ulaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ iki handeteke hataęž‰ hatuku ombu pu hoeyaemeke ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone ambaęž‰ wilimime. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande pi lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ale manunaęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ pemekeeki loaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone uemenaęž‰yeke do alome. Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ hoeyaenaęž‰e laa pi lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ make Yesutaęž‰ otaęž‰ Tekehalie laa loluekemaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ na handeteke haenaęž‰ kone kutupiki pi lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 4 Hande Sipitidinaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo kitaęž‰laęž‰ Sipitiditaęž‰ homeke kone halaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Mo Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokaasomaęž‰ ekimanu make taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo enaęž‰ Tekehalitaęž‰ homeke kone halaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kutupa ipikaęž‰ e pokaenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo e pokaapeke handaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pate pa homeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone koto e pokaasaęž‰ haumanu paeyaotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ teli peaasaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Wandaęž‰hali paeyao epeaaluekemaęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ niki paeyao homeke homeke paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pitaasaęž‰eki walaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 8 Hande Sipitidimaęž‰ hali homeke paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hone wiki pi alaęž‰eki halolo hataęž‰ mo homeke Sipitidimaęž‰ kone hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make epeke handaasaęž‰eki halaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 9 Do homeke Sipitidimaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰eki halaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo homeke Sipitidimaęž‰ kone hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mo yeni haaseme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni tandelaasaęž‰eki halaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Mo Sipitidimaęž‰ hali homeke paęž‰taęž‰ mo na handeke hau manunaęž‰ peaęž‰peke wele halaataęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walaasaęž‰eki halaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo kitaęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰eki o hoke temokomaęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰eki tekili pea pa handenaęž‰yeke peaasaęž‰eki halaęž‰laęž‰me. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mo taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰piki pimanu alaęž‰eki halaataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ kutupiki pimanu opua pa laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wele halaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ hande homeke Sipitidimaęž‰ kone wandaęž‰hali homeke homeke paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone telipaaso hataęž‰ peaasaęž‰me.   
\s1 Loke homekemaęž‰ kone alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao haasaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 12 Ketisotaęž‰ loke homeke tupaęž‰ kiki ankemanu tuna tuna pea halaęž‰me. Hande kiki anke lokenaęž‰ tunaalaęž‰ alemanu taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate loketaęž‰ homeke kone halaęž‰me.  
