\c 13  
\s1 Pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pimanu make mo enisolo titinaęž‰ pi make alo hali hataęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau na pitolo hataęž‰ laęž‰tiki pu haowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka pi aloeki manutaęž‰ mo beto pa litaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handekeeki o pa ti kaęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ kaęž‰kaęž‰paęž‰ laasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handekeeki kone alome.  
