\c 14  
\s1 Mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ ale manunaęž‰ mandane pimanu  
\p
\v 1 Koto ekinaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau puluekemaęž‰ honkopu hao hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu muluekemaęž‰ hone wotu wiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate hande pa mo kitaęž‰laęž‰eki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea haloemenaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone ambaęž‰la wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
