\v 3 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ la halaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea haleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ pi make ikaęž‰ puki epeaasaęž‰ pi make epekeeki pinaęž‰ sutiaasaęž‰ pi make alaęž‰me.  
