\p
\v 5 Iki paeyaomaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki pi alaęž‰eki pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo polopate iki paeyaomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halaęž‰laęž‰eki pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homulueke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± mo da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki pi leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pimaęž‰taęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ lenaęž‰ pa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo somenaęž‰ pi na laęž‰kaęž‰leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ mo siosi epeaasaęž‰ hali na haliepate pa mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hau tieke yelieke.  
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ kametitio. IĚ±taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa mo da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki pimanu kone loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ekipa tambaęž‰ muluepe. Diaęž‰me. Iki na tambaęž‰ mulueke. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ la kitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ make handoloeki mandane ekimanu make iki paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea kulu poloeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ make pi walo poloeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ make kutupiki pimanu laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke.   
\p
