\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu muluekemaęž‰ hone wopu peleme ekinaęž‰yeke kotaęž‰ mo hande siosi wandaęž‰hali daenaęž‰ lapeke ekimanu otaęž‰ titinaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ mea puluekemaęž‰ honkopu hao hapaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pi lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ somemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ pi laęž‰kaęž‰lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ hau make muluekemaęž‰ yeni peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 14 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ mo da taęž‰taęž‰ piki pimaęž‰ yeni puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka temokomaęž‰ kone yeni pitolopate yaka honemaęž‰ na pitolome.  
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ eki haumanu puluaęž‰pe. Yaka temokomaęž‰ yeni pulu polopate pa yaka honemaęž‰ make yeni pulueke. Emelitaęž‰ yaka temokomaęž‰ lolo polopate pa yaka honemaęž‰ make lolueke.  
\v 16 Neketaęž‰ pa nakaęž‰ temoko homekemaęž‰ da taęž‰taęž‰ piki pimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi laa yeni pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo iki ameĚ±leĚ± pilaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hande da taęž‰taęž‰ piki pi ale ekitaęž‰ na opiki hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Aowe. Kutu pinaęž‰e laa ekipa opua lenaęž‰pe.  
\v 17 Neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi alepatetaęž‰ mo halitaęž‰ na tambaęž‰ mineleme.   
\p
\v 18 Do hande da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pi alaęž‰ hautaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ alo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki paeyao ankulao halo ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi alome.  
\v 19 Pate hande siosi wandaęž‰hali mombeleme ekinaęž‰ hataęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi waluekemaęž‰ mo iki opuaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ pi dokaęž‰tiki yunki hataęž‰manu homeke loluekemaęž‰ waleke wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pimaęž‰ otaęž‰ hokulupeke 10 daoseni pimanu waluekemaęž‰ hone na wiki kiaalueke.   
\p
\v 20 Kametitio. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wekisunumaęž‰ witeleme hone leke wia na hapaęž‰peke. Hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ wekisunu leke hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa ikaęž‰ hone witeleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ keileke wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ witeleme hone leke wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 21 Mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupa  
\q1 Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo mandane da maęž‰ndaęž‰ pi leke haliwekimaęž‰ aleme ekimaęž‰ make mo da maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane hao epeleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ do wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi loluepate pa kutupiki hau kone puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi pa na opilimikie  
\m laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 22 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Sipitidimaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pi alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo pi mineleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰eki diaęž‰me. Pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo pi na miki wandaęž‰hali patehau pinaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tombo ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pi na miki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opinaęž‰yeke na kiki pi mineleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opinaęž‰yeke kaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 23 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ mombela pitaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pimanu lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mandane pa aęž‰pa haleme wandaęž‰hali o pi na miki wandaęž‰hali make hondaęž‰ pamba mo pi manutaęž‰ opitolo hataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Do wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ keaaso alememe laa lelimikie.  
\v 24 Koto lolo pelemepate mo siosi wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea halelemeeki pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa aęž‰pa pilaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ o pi na miki hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pitaęž‰ kutupiki pi opitolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hone wilieke. Kutupa mo laęž‰ mea halaęž‰laęž‰ pi opitolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ epekeeki make hokeeki make hone wilieke.  
\v 25 Koto ekinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰ honemanu peneme yaeyeke handaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pandaęž‰puniao Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitolo hataęž‰ Otaęž‰ alememe. Kodaęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± do paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me laa lelieke.   
\s1 Siosi mombelemeeki paęž‰taęž‰ tiki tiki yao pulu peaęž‰pekeeki  
\p
\v 26 Ya kametitio. Eki haumanu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰ mombelemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ emeli lelieke. Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ pi walelieke. Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ la halaęž‰laęž‰eki iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kilieke. Kutupa hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pi laa leliepate hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ koto alaęž‰ pi lekelieke. Kutu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate mo hau paeyaomaęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰hali epeaaluekemaęž‰ pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epelieke.  
\v 27 Mandane haliwekimaęž‰ da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰ hone pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hali yaapo tepomaęž‰ homeke lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ pilieke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mandake dinaęž‰ na lelimikie. Kutupa ikaęž‰ aleme pitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰lenaęž‰ otaęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 28 Kutu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate mo pi laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ hali na hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo mombaęž‰la pilaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki pimaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ na lelieke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homeke pi lelieke.  
\v 29 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰eki mineleme hali yaapo tepomaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ mineleme pimanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa opiteleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ alemeeki opua honemaęž‰ mo otaęž‰eki weilimikie.  
\v 30 Kutupa mo mombaęž‰la pilaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo la halaęž‰laęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± koto kone haleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hande tiao pi walaęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ lo naenaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 31 Siosi wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opua minolo hataęž‰ hone wopu wia honkopu hao haenaęž‰yeke iki paeyaomaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ lo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ la kitaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 32 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ mea haleleme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ koto iki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ temokomanu handeteke hamenaęž‰e laa hone wiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 33 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ meimei liao na hake pa yopu sembepelao hamonoyeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki wi laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\p Mo hande siosi wandaęž‰hali mombolo hataęž‰ pu haleme tupaęž‰  
\v 34 wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰taęž‰ pi pi na leke pa pitaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Hande Lo Pi manumaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰taęž‰ pi walaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ homu pea hao hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 35 Wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pa lotaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ halikititi paęž‰taęž‰ lotaęž‰ peaęž‰peke aleo. Siosi wandaęž‰hali paeyao mombaęž‰la pitinaęž‰ wandaęž‰maęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ti na pilieke.   
\p
\v 36 Kutaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ kini pea opolo epeekepe o iki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 37 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walolo hali hataęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ make ambaęž‰ molome hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto somemaęž‰taęž‰ do IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ wape polo ekitaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ dupaęž‰pe laa laęž‰laęž‰ ekie laa hone winaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 38 Kutu peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pate koto some epimaęž‰ do alo ekimanu na opiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mo halinaęž‰ pi na opuaęž‰paęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 39 Koto ekinaęž‰ ya kametitio. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi waluekemaęž‰ honkopu hao hataęž‰ kone pa mo da taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pimanu alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ na peaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 40 Kutupa ikaęž‰ pitelemeeki paeyaotaęž‰ tiki tiki yao hataęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke.   
\c 15  
\s1 Yesu paa tiaeyekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Ya kametitio. Ame IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰ Pi Seliapotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone u tiaaluekemaęž‰ alome. Koto pimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ meataęž‰ hone tulao honkopu hao haminaęž‰ iki mea daęž‰taalaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Hande Pi Seliapotaęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰ pi kone loaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ honkopu hao wopu miniki haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pimaęž‰ iki homaapaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ milieke. Kotaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pi pa hameke opimikaęž‰taęž‰me.   
\p
\v 3 Mo hande pi teke tieketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ muaęž‰ pi kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ la kuaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Ketisotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke haunaęž‰ homeekeme. Koto mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Kutupa ipiki toko toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lapaęž‰ pimikipate hoto teponaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ paa mea tiaeyekeme. Kutu pieke ekimanu make mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ piekeme.  
\v 5 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Pida paęž‰taęž‰ pua ipikaęž‰ loke peneme yao walaataęž‰ mo hande 12 aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make pua waleekeme.  
\v 6 Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ mo mandake paęž‰taęž‰ mombaęž‰la haleme nikaęž‰ kametiti 500manu paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki pua waleekeme. Mo hande haliwekitaęž‰ mandane ekitaęž‰ homemekepate mandane haliweki woputaęž‰ pa hao halememe.  
\v 7 Kutupa koto hoki nanetaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Diaęž‰mesi paęž‰taęž‰ pua walaataęž‰ mo aposolo haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make paa pua waleekeme.   
\p
\v 8 Otaęž‰ wetepe nanetaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kone aęž‰pa waleaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ hande mu hoeyaasaęž‰ weki leke hano kone aęž‰pa waleaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Mo aposolo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ hosiki halisiki halome. Koto biki muluekemaęž‰ epeke hali na haowaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ siosi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tanda tieke haloaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Kutu puaęž‰pate ame pa IĚ± do halo ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pa hameke aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ peaalaęž‰me. Kutupa koto ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ wele na piki paekie laa pi lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ honkopu hao ipikaęž‰ e pokaaso hataęž‰ mo hande aposolo haliweki paeyao kone wetepeaowaęž‰me. Kutu puaęž‰pate IĚ±maęž‰ ya kone na puaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pitaęž‰ peaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ puaęž‰ekipe o mo aposolo haliwekimaęž‰ pimiekipe pa mataęž‰laęž‰pate do walolo ekitaęž‰ niki paeyaomaęž‰ walolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ homeke kone kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opuataęž‰ hone tulaalememe.   
\s1 Niki paa tiaalo polomaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ homeekepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa mea tiaeyekeeki walo halomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ haleme mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Mo ambaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ paa mea tiaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me la aleme ekitaęž‰ ekipeke alemepe.  
\v 13 Koto aleme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi lemekaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make Ketiso na mea tiaalo piaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kutupa make Ketisotaęž‰ na mea tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ walaęž‰peke na yolo piaęž‰me. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaapeke na yolo piaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Kutupa niki make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Ketiso paa mea tiaeyekeeki walomeke handaataęž‰ yayapiki pi alomaęž‰ haliweki halo pumaęž‰me. Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali paa na mea tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Ketiso make na mea tiaalo piaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Ambaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa na mea tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Ketiso make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa na mea tiaalo piaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Kutupa Ketiso paa na mea tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaaleme ekitaęž‰ pa aleme handolo piaęž‰me. Kutupa ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu make paa ulu piaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Kutupa Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hao homemeke wandaęž‰hali make otaęž‰ alu pulu pimime.  
\v 19 Nikaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hataęž‰ handeteke halomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ halomaęž‰eki homeke yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰la aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke aleo.   
\p
\v 20 Kutu pulu piaęž‰pate kotoeki diaęž‰me. Otaęž‰eki dupae. Ketisotaęž‰ homeekepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa mea tiaeyekeme. Puki napeke ne tupaęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ mea tiaeyeke halie.  
\v 21 Homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hali homeke paęž‰taęž‰ epeeke tupaęž‰ kotaęž‰ homaa paa tiaalo polomaęž‰eki make hali homeke paęž‰taęž‰ epeekeme.  
\v 22 Kotaęž‰ mo Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ homeleme tupaęž‰ pa mo Ketisonaęž‰ tapake wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa mea tiaalieke.  
\v 23 Kutu piliepate pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ lelie natenaęž‰ kone paa tiaalieke. Dupae. Hande puki napeke ne tupaęž‰ Ketiso titinaęž‰e. Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ mo Ketisonaęž‰ ipilie natenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali mea tiaalieke.  
\v 24 Kutu pilie dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo paeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰eki pilieke. Ketisomaęž‰taęž‰ mo handeteke haleme haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ piteleme ekimanu make mo you haliweki paeyaomaęž‰ piteleme ekimanu make wele piteleme ekimanu paeyao make ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ paeyao bepolaotaęž‰ hande Kilu Tumbuao Halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Ateke Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea halieke.  
\v 25 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliweki paeyao kone anaęž‰naęž‰ lu tombuao haluekemaęž‰taęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ otaęž‰ you hali hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 26 Kutupataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki alemanu lu paeyaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki kone ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ bepolaaso hataęž‰ paeyaalieke.  
\v 27 Kotaęž‰ mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa. Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao ipikaęž‰ anke oto paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mea wiaalaęž‰me laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me. Do Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao Ketisonaęž‰ anke oto paęž‰taęž‰ mea wiaalaęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa Kodaęž‰ kone Ketisonaęž‰ anke oto paęž‰taęž‰ wialaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ na laęž‰laęž‰me hone witolomaęž‰me.  
\v 28 Diaęž‰me. Alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao Ketisomaęž‰ kilu tombuao hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone Eiyeke hataęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ anke oto paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao mea wiaeyeke Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki kone oto paęž‰taęž‰ halieke. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ paeyao tapao manda hataęž‰ otaęž‰ kilu tombuao halieke.   
\p
\v 29 Pate Paa na tiaalumekee lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ bapitaisi piteleme hautaęž‰ eki puluekemaęž‰ koto hau pitelemepe. Ambaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali paa mea tiaapeke na yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ ekipeke bapitaisi hau pitelemepe.  
\v 30 Kutupa niki make pa ekipeke nikaęž‰ loke otaęž‰ hoeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰ alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ hao halomaęž‰pe.  
\v 31 Ya kametitio. Homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nate paeyao IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Dotaęž‰ pa yapaęž‰piki pi alope. Diaęž‰me. Nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pea halomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi laaso hataęž‰ pitolo tupaęž‰ do alo pi make otaęž‰ekie alome.  
\v 32 IĚ±maęž‰ do Epesese da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ mandane sayalemanu paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ piki nono puaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto puaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± ekipa tambaęž‰ miliepe. Pate ambaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali paa mea tiaapeke na yeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo  
\q1 Belia tuneke homolo polomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ame ne ikali naa keamanaęž‰ pipe laa  
\m lo haleme ekinaęž‰ niki make lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 33 Makeaasaęž‰eki na opuaęž‰paęž‰peke. Hoke wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± pomumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ epeke hau pitolomaęž‰eki hoeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 34 Ikaęž‰ hoke hau piteleme ekimanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao ikaęž‰ hone tiki tiki yao epeke tupaęž‰ paa hapaęž‰peke. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ haleme mandane wandaęž‰hali manumaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau na handelememe. Do alo ekinaęž‰taęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homaaminaęž‰ alome.   
\s1 Nikaęž‰ paa tiaalo polomaęž‰ loke  
\p
\v 35 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ dupa lotaęž‰ pilieke. Homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ paa mea tiaake hautaęž‰ ekipape o pa ekipiki loke halimipe laa lotaęž‰ pilieke.  
\v 36 Neketaęž‰ hone na wiki someo. Wae ale homeke kenkenaęž‰ pa nokepeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ aeyeke homaataęž‰ paa opilieke.  
\v 37 Kutupa kenkenaęž‰ nokaęž‰pele aletaęž‰ pa wae alesiki nokaęž‰pilipikie. Palaowa wae alesiki o wae alesiki maęž‰ndaęž‰pe mataęž‰laęž‰pate hande opolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na nokaęž‰peleme.  
\v 38 Hande wae ale sikitaęž‰ opolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ peaasaęž‰me. Mo wae ale taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pikieki manunaęž‰ opolo paęž‰laęž‰eki make taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ peaasaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 39 Kutupa do kenkenaęž‰ daęž‰ta halaęž‰eki manunaęž‰ loke mindikitaęž‰ homeke tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰eki taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa maęž‰naęž‰ yeti ba taęž‰peli manunaęž‰eki taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 40 Kutupa ya nane alemanu make kenke nane alemanu make halememe. Oli ya nane ale manunaęž‰ seliapo piki au laęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa kenke nane ale manunaęž‰ seliapo piki au laęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 41 Oli natetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ au laęž‰laęž‰eki taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa oli sumbaęž‰naęž‰eki make oli hombulankaęž‰ manunaęž‰eki make taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa make oli hombulankaęž‰ manunaęž‰ au lelemeeki make taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 42 Kutupa mo hande homemeke wandaęž‰hali paa mea tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ kone halumeke. Hali toko hoitolo haenaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ale ulaęž‰me. Paa mea tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰eki halieke.  
\v 43 Hoitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ pa hoke alemaęž‰ handaataęž‰ honkopu na hao witaęž‰laęž‰pate kone paa mea tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ epekeeki hataęž‰ honkopu hao halieke.  
\v 44 Hoitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ kenke loke homeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate paa mea tiaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa epeke temokonaęž‰eki halieke. Do kenkenaęž‰ loke mindiki halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kotaęž‰ pa mo epeke epeke temokonaęž‰eki make otaęž‰ halieke.  
\v 45 Mo Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa. Ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hali Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wepia daęž‰ta haenaęž‰ leeke halie wape paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo wetepe nane Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo deto haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ Temokoe.  
\v 46 Epeke temokonaęž‰eki ambaęž‰la haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ eki diaęž‰me. Do kenke loke ambaęž‰la haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo epeke temokonaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰e.  
\v 47 Titinaęž‰ Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kenke dokolomaęž‰ wepia haenaęž‰ leeke halie. Namba 2 Aęž‰daęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hepeni nane hao epeeke halie.  
\v 48 Do kenkenaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hande kenkenaęž‰ wepia haenaęž‰ leeke halimaęž‰ handelememe. Kutupa mo hepeni nane halo peleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hande hepeni nane hao epeeke halimaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me.  
\v 49 Ametaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hande kenkemaęž‰ wepia haenaęž‰ leeke halimaęž‰ handolomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kotaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ mo hepeni nane hao epeeke halimaęž‰ handulumeke.   
\p
\v 50 Kametitio. Do ekinaęž‰ alome. Loke mindiki wemaęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ pua hapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa homaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki meaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 51 Do la kitolomaęž‰ aęž‰mbaasaęž‰ pitaęž‰ opuaęž‰pe. Niki paeyao otaęž‰ na homolo polomaęž‰pate pa mo paeyaaso haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ bu kanake litolo hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰  
\v 52 nikitaęž‰ leke handu handu pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ kuta kone wonu pila halumeke. Hande bu kanake liaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mea tiao paa na homolo peleme wandaęž‰hali halimikie. Kutupa niki paeyao wonu pila halumeke.  
\v 53 Do alu peaęž‰peke loketaęž‰ topo pitolo hataęž‰ pa mo hao halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ yamilieke. Kutupa do homo halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ topo pitolo hataęž‰ pa mo deto halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ yamilieke.  
\v 54 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo alu peaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ pa mo hao halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ yamiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kutupa mo homo halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa mo deto halaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ yamiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hande Baibolo bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaalieke. Dupa.  
\q1 Homo halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰ laęž‰pa paęž‰laęž‰me. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ bepolaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ bepolaęž‰pa paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\q1
\v 55 Homaęž‰laęž‰ekio. Nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali pa homao bepolaalo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handope.  
\q1 Homaęž‰laęž‰ekio. Nakaęž‰ tanda peao homaaluekemaęž‰ wele peaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ handope  
\m laa wape paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 56 Homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tanda peao homaaluekemaęž‰ wele peaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ mu halaęž‰me. Kutupa hoke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wele peaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hande Lo Pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ mu halaęž‰me.  
\v 57 Kutu pitaęž‰laęž‰pate nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi lomanaęž‰e. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Tekehali Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ mo tombuao bepolaeyekeeki niki paęž‰taęž‰ ku halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 58 Koto ekinaęž‰ otaęž‰ ya kametonuo. DaĚ±oĚ±la hataęž‰ takaęž‰lao hapaęž‰peke. Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokaaseme ekitaęž‰ nate wotu pokaatiki pu hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokaaseme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ homekesiki kone na alupeaęž‰peke yaęž‰leke handa loaęž‰me.   
\c 16  
\s1 Ketiso tapakemanu tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ mani  
\p
\v 1 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo mandane Diutuseleme haleme Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ mani amu pulu peleme ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Kaęž‰leisia kenke nane haleme siosimanu paęž‰taęž‰ Dupaęž‰pe laa loaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make peaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 2 Sande paeyaonaęž‰ iki paeyaonaęž‰ homeke homeke lo ambaęž‰ pulanaęž‰ melemeeki dimina handaataęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ putupa pa mandaneeki ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ wiaęž‰tiki pu hapaęž‰peke. Koto ekinaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ IĚ± epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mani weiyaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me.  
\v 3 IĚ± opolo epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tiki tiki yao wimi manitaęž‰ mo talopu mea haenaęž‰ leleme haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ Diutuseleme nane mea puaenaęž‰yeke IĚ±maęž‰ pasemanu wape pea halaataęž‰ tapaalueke.  
\v 4 IĚ± make polueke hone uaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ niki mandakenaęž‰ polumeke.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ pulu piekeeki  
\p
\v 5 IĚ±maęž‰ Maęž‰sedonia nanemaęž‰ laalaęž‰ puataęž‰ iki haleme alenaęž‰ opolo ipulueke. Maęž‰sedonia nane ambaęž‰la puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me loaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Iki ameĚ±leĚ± hosiki hao haluekemaęž‰ hone witolopate pa mataęž‰laęž‰me. Mo kosaęž‰ ki paeyaonaęž‰ halumaęž‰pe. Kutupa wetepenaęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ nane poaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ potaęž‰ IĚ± tapaaminaęž‰e hone witolome.  
\v 7 Iki ameĚ±leĚ± pa taęž‰kaęž‰li hamanaęž‰ hone na witolome. Tekehalimaęž‰ hone piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± nate wopu haluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Kutu pulu polopatetaęž‰ hande Pendikosi nate epenaęž‰ do Epesese da paęž‰taęž‰ handeteke halueke.  
\v 9 Do ekinaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me. Do paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ potaęž‰ lombaęž‰pa ulaęž‰me. Kutupa epeke epeke e tieke tieke pokaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu pulu polopate pa mo potaęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pulu peleme haliweki wotu make halememe.   
\p
\v 10 Timodi iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki epeke tupaęž‰ handaęž‰ mea epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ pitolo tupaęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Kutupa hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ honditi hone na wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ tapaapaęž‰peke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mandane Ketiso yankeketiti ameĚ±leĚ± do ane epenaęž‰yeke handeteke halome.   
\p
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰ nikaęž‰ kame Apolositaęž‰ mo mandane kametiti ameĚ±leĚ± iki handolo penaęž‰yeke hoto eleke eleke sutiaatiki puaęž‰pate pa ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ ame do kone aĚ±iĚ± handolo puaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Wetepenaęž‰ nate anaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki handolo pelieke.   
\s1 Paeyaaso pimanu  
\p
\v 13 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kokele pea hataęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ make daĚ±oĚ±la hao hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa puki hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰pa hataęž‰ honkopu hao hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ piteleme haumanu paeyaotaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ pu hapaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 15 Some maęž‰ndaęž‰ Sitepanisitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki wandaęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handelememe. Koto tapaketaęž‰ mo Akaya Potobinisi nane hataęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ pi mea hataęž‰ pa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ e pokaatiki pitelememe. Koto ekinaęž‰ ya kametiti iki paęž‰taęž‰ honke alo hataęž‰ dupa alome.  
\v 16 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto tapake make mo ikaęž‰ mandake e pokaaseme wandaęž‰hali make iki oto paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hao hapaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 17 Mo tepo halitaęž‰ Sitepanisi Potunatasi Akaikusi ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epeleme ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolome. Iki paeyaotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰peke na yeaęž‰pate do hali tepotaęž‰ iki epolo pimi tupaęž‰ epelememe.  
\v 18 Koto haliwekimaęž‰ iki taęž‰naęž‰ peaalaęž‰ tupaęž‰ IĚ± make taęž‰naęž‰ peaasememe. Kutu piki haliweki manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi laapaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 19 Mo Eisia Potobinisi nane haleme siosi manumaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo keiyae pi laęž‰niaasememe. Hande Akuila Pisila toolimaęž‰ make ipilikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ mombolo haleme siosi ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ keiyae pi make laęž‰niaasememe.  
\v 20 Do paęž‰taęž‰ halomaęž‰ kametitimaęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo keiyae pi laęž‰niaasememe. Mombelemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone hopula alu alu peaęž‰paęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 21 Yaka kikimaęž‰ kone IĚ±taęž‰ Polomaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae pi laęž‰niaasome laa do wape pea polome.  
\v 22 Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ na homeke pa kiaasaęž‰ hali epitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyaenaęž‰e. Nikaęž‰ Tekehalio. Epoe.  
\v 23 Mo Tekehali Yesunaęž‰ pa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰e.  
\v 24 IĚ±maęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰taęž‰ iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolome.   